RelatedSentence: A new study , led by Judith Gordon , associate head of research for the Department of Family and Community Medicine at the UA College of Medicine - Tucson , will develop and test a mobile phone application designed to help women stop smoking while learning to eat more healthfully and increasing their physical activity .
The National Cancer Institute has awarded $ 365,000  for the two - year project .
In the first phase of the study , 10 to 20 Tucson - area women who want to quit smoking but are worried about weight gain will review the app and provide feedback .
